    {
        "content": "<p>I was actually gonna ask - how would you feel about trying Bow Market just one time before summer/fall is up? Not for another hackathon, just as a location for a meeting? We never really took advantage of it, being cooped up in that room for the power outlets. Similar to Time Out, it has food options and beer (and coffee).</p>\n<p>Downsides include no nearby train stops, and potentially being stuck indoors anyway in case of rain (in which case could you bring food into that brewery? I dunno.)</p>\n<p>(thinking about it more - I think Time Out would be a better place if we did another hackathon. Lots more indoor space.)</p>",
        "id": 609646426,
        "sender_full_name": "Dan",
        "timestamp": 1783813815
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm definitely ok with mixing up the location. I like Time Out but there are plenty of other nice places.</p>",
        "id": 609690604,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin",
        "timestamp": 1783861885
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"655359\">Dan</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/406743-boston/topic/2026-08.20meetup/near/609646426\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>no nearby train stops</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The closest T stop to Bow Market is the somewhat new Union Square stop, an 8 minute walk for 0.4 miles:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2026-07-12 at 9.14.44 AM.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"2372x1048\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/56571/cSqD2JYtLjtwYjo2EJPGn4gL/Screenshot-2026-07-12-at-9.14.44AM.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/56571/cSqD2JYtLjtwYjo2EJPGn4gL/Screenshot-2026-07-12-at-9.14.44AM.png/840x560.webp\"></p>",
        "id": 609691086,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin",
        "timestamp": 1783862169
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Next closest  is the East Somerville, a 17 minute walk for 0.7 miles:<br>\n<img alt=\"Screenshot 2026-07-12 at 9.17.50 AM.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"2372x1048\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/56571/0KoKrd1UFbu5DOLKhRDmLCDT/Screenshot-2026-07-12-at-9.17.50AM.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/56571/0KoKrd1UFbu5DOLKhRDmLCDT/Screenshot-2026-07-12-at-9.17.50AM.png/840x560.webp\"></p>",
        "id": 609691343,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin",
        "timestamp": 1783862331
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>In comparison, Time Out is only a 3 minute walk for 0.1 miles from the Fenway stop:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2026-07-12 at 9.20.24 AM.png\" class=\"inline-image\" data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"2372x1048\" data-original-src=\"/user_uploads/56571/99VNz8Ie8PoTN7mXHZ70dL5W/Screenshot-2026-07-12-at-9.20.24AM.png\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/56571/99VNz8Ie8PoTN7mXHZ70dL5W/Screenshot-2026-07-12-at-9.20.24AM.png/840x560.webp\"></p>",
        "id": 609691554,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin",
        "timestamp": 1783862472
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Well I'd be curious what others think. If nobody is enthusiastic about it I'm happy to withdraw my suggestion.</p>",
        "id": 609696267,
        "sender_full_name": "Dan",
        "timestamp": 1783867335
    },
    {
